  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve ever-changing puzzles as you delve deeper and deeper in the prehistoric underground playing as Anzu!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect as many resources and treasures to buy upgrades in the hub! Also make sure to start hatching some dinosaur eggs in your hatchery for some extra treasures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You'll need to use everything at your disposal to appease the gods and make sure to stay alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Build your hatchery in the hub and hatch your eggs to collect more treasure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place eggs on top of nests or incubators to start hatching eggs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match-4 objects in the hub to fuse and upgrade your hatchery equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the different parts of the hub to unlock even more upgrades! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come by the shop, It might sell some useful items to take your run to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore and rebuild the museum and discover the unknown artifacts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the puzzle to gather more resources and challenge yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful... The gods will throw everything at their disposal to take you out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features summarized: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve ever-changing puzzles</strong> playing as Anzu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> the hub</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore & rebuild</strong> the Museum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong> the puzzle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hatch eggs</strong> in the hatchery for extra rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fuse</strong> building blocks into better versions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock a special character</strong> to play as</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face dangerous challenges</strong> that progressively get harder throughout the game</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve ever-changing puzzles as you delve deeper and deeper in the prehistoric underground playing as Anzu!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect as many resources and treasures to buy upgrades in the hub! Also make sure to start hatching some dinosaur eggs in your hatchery for some extra treasures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You'll need to use everything at your disposal to appease the gods and make sure to stay alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/c98f013379d44a8f4c9cb6eca43d1fb9.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Build your hatchery in the hub and hatch your eggs to collect more treasure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place eggs on top of nests or incubators to start hatching eggs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match-4 objects in the hub to fuse and upgrade your hatchery equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/30d1d55222f4bbed06315c2dbc495602.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the different parts of the hub to unlock even more upgrades! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come by the shop, It might sell some useful items to take your run to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore and rebuild the museum and discover the unknown artifacts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/16ce0d3e6915680e95474ef9f3805184.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the puzzle to gather more resources and challenge yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be careful... The gods will throw everything at their disposal to take you out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.poster.avif?t=1734019923\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.webm?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332880/extras/d066d11544f385c4bcbebbea4b42db4a.mp4?t=1734019923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features summarized: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve ever-changing puzzles</strong> playing as Anzu.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> the hub</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore & rebuild</strong> the Museum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong> the puzzle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hatch eggs</strong> in the hatchery for extra rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fuse</strong> building blocks into better versions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock a special character</strong> to play as</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face dangerous challenges</strong> that progressively get harder throughout the game</p></li></ul>",
